<h2 style="color: #1f2937; margin-top: 0;">{{subject}}</h2>
<p style="color: #4b5563;">{{content}}</p>
{{#if title}}
<div style="background-color: #f0f9ff; padding: 16px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 16px 0; border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6;">
  <p style="margin: 0; font-weight: 600; color: #1e40af;">{{title}}</p>
  {{#if companyName}}<p style="margin: 4px 0 0; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px;">{{companyName}}</p>{{/if}}
</div>
{{/if}}
<a href="{{actionUrl}}" class="btn" style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #3b82f6; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600;">잡차자에서 확인하기</a>
<p style="color: #9ca3af; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 16px;">본 메일은 잡차자에서 자동 발송되었습니다.</p>
